Package: mobilityIndexR
Type: Package
Title: Calculates Transition Matrices and Mobility Indices
Version: 0.1.5
Author: Brett Mullins and Trevor Harkreader
Maintainer: Brett Mullins <brettcmullins@gmail.com>
Description: This package measures mobility in a population through transition matrices and mobility indices. Relative, mixed, and absolute transition matrices are supported for various use cases. With respect to indices, the Prais-Bibby, Absolute Movement, Origin Specific, and Shorrocks indices are supported. Example income and grade data are included for demos.
